{
  "id": "adv_event_2309_01_04_01",
  "title": "優し過ぎます",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_press-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――ユニットバトル、組み合わせ抽選会当日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――On the day of the unit battle pairings lottery",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "endTime": 1.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gaya-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 1.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "わぁ、出場者が沢山\n見たことのある人もかなり多いわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow‚ there are so many participants.\nI see a lot of familiar faces.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.63333354,
      "endTime": 9.7046033383,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "サヤ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saya",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04-saya001.m4a",
      "text": "どうも～。びっくりしましたよ、まさかあの\nBIG4のサニピのお二人がいるなんて～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hi there~. I was surprised. To think that\nthe two of you from Sunny Peace‚ a BIG4 group‚ are here~.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.9149885337,
      "endTime": 19.5749900978,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_press-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 19.7816567262
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "お手柔らかにお願いしますね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Please go easy on us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.7816567262,
      "endTime": 22.184695275600003,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_press-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 22.395080471
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "（この人達……最近ライブバトルで連勝中で）\n（話題になってるグループの人だ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（These girls… They’ve been on a winning streak in live battles recently‚）\n（and they’re the group that’s been the talk of the town.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.395080471,
      "endTime": 29.9950806617,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_press-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 30.2054658571
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "アヤ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aya",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04-aya001.m4a",
      "text": "それにしてもびっくりだよね～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s so surprising‚ don’t you think~?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.2054658571,
      "endTime": 39.8617473284,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "アヤ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aya",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "「あの」佐伯遙子さんが今やBIG4なんて～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "“That” Haruko Saeki is now in the BIG4~.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.7284120718,
      "endTime": 40.1721323648,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_press-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 40.3721322695
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "……どういう意味ですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…What do you mean?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.3721322695,
      "endTime": 43.1545586745,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "アヤ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aya",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04-aya002.m4a",
      "text": "だって、あの頃はもういるかどうかも分かんない\nくらい存在感なかったもんね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ back then‚ she had such a small presence\nthat you couldn’t tell if she was even there.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.3649438698,
      "endTime": 51.4649378616,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "サヤ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saya",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04-saya002.m4a",
      "text": "ソロで冴えなくても、良さげなグループさえ組めば",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If a solo career doesn’t work out‚ you can just form a decent group",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.6649377663,
      "endTime": 60.8974550087,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "サヤ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saya",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "売れちゃうんだから……運がいいよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and become popular… She’s so lucky.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.2333333333,
      "endTime": 61.028409783,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_press-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 61.2649377663
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "……何を勝手なこと……\nあなた達に遙子さんの何が分かって――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Don’t talk nonsense…\nWhat do you know about Haruko-san――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.2649377663,
      "endTime": 67.3003348191,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_press-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 67.2773871898
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "怜ちゃん、それ以上言わなくていいわ\n言いたい人には言わせておけばいいのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rei‚ you don’t have to say anything more.\nJust let them say whatever they want.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.2773871898,
      "endTime": 73.37738738050001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_press-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 73.5877725759
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さん！？　でも……！\nこんなこと言われて悔しくないんですか！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haruko-san!? But…!\nAren’t you angry after hearing something like that!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.5877725759,
      "endTime": 80.4377727665,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_press-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 80.6481579619
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "私が売れてなかったのは事実だしね\n地味で存在感ないのも自覚はあるし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s true that I wasn’t popular‚\nand I’m aware that I’m plain and have no presence.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.6481579619,
      "endTime": 87.39654796880001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_press-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 87.6069331643
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "サヤ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saya",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04-saya003.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ？　なになに、寛容アピールの上に",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? What‚ after acting all tolerant‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.6069331643,
      "endTime": 98.1390872476,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "サヤ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saya",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "自虐で可愛らしさアピールですか～？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "now you’re trying to appear cute by putting yourself down~?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.1642370381,
      "endTime": 98.40693173369999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_press-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 98.6069316384
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "……いい加減にして\n遙子さんをバカにするのは、私が許さない！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Enough is enough.\nI won’t forgive you for making fun of Haruko-san!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.6069316384,
      "endTime": 105.6653215881,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "今ここで宣言するわ\nあなた達も倒して、私と遙子さんが優勝する！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m making a declaration here and now.\nI’ll defeat you‚ and Haruko-san and I will win this tournament!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.8757067836,
      "endTime": 114.0087680019,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_press-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 114.2191531972
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "アヤ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aya",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04-aya003.m4a",
      "text": "へ～、宣言とかかっこい～。確かにサニピはBIG4に\nなったけど、五人揃ってるからこその強さでしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Whoa‚ a declaration? So cool. Sure‚ Sunny Peace might be in the BIG4‚\nbut their strength comes from having all five members together‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.2191531972,
      "endTime": 128.73333333329998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_press-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 128.9524865307
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "サヤ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saya",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04-saya004.m4a",
      "text": "あんた達二人だけなら、負ける気がしないわ\n実際に戦ってみれば分かるわよ。それじゃ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If it’s just the two of you‚ I don’t think we’ll lose.\nWe’ll see when we actually battle. Later.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.9524865307,
      "endTime": 137.3124774136,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3335.768048200009
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04-rei007.m4a",
      "text": "この……っ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.519144042,
      "endTime": 139.4182143526,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_press-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 139.628599548
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04-rei008.m4a",
      "text": "（遙子さんは優しい……それは分かってる。でも）\n（あんな酷いことを言われて怒らないなんて……っ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Haruko-san is kind… I know that. But…）\n（How can she not be angry after being told such awful things…!）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.628599548,
      "endTime": 150.68104858360002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_press-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 147.5308986185
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ、はぁ、はぁ……っ！　……ふぅ\nかなりいい感じじゃない？　今日はこれくらいにする？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Pant‚ pant‚ pant…! …Phew.\nWe’re doing pretty well‚ aren’t we? Should we stop here for today?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 156.9914246238,
      "endTime": 167.98936068170002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04-rei009.m4a",
      "text": "何言ってるんですか？　こんなのまだ全然ですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What are you saying? This isn’t nearly enough.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 167.9333333333,
      "endTime": 172.66666666670002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04-hrk006.m4a",
      "text": "怜ちゃん……体は大丈夫？\n最近オフの日にもずっと練習してるでしょう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rei… Are you alright?\nYou’ve been practicing even on your days off lately.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 172.9874729152,
      "endTime": 180.67747278169998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04-rei010.m4a",
      "text": "……大会が近いんだから、それくらい当たり前です\n遙子さんは甘過ぎます。足を引っ張らないで下さい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…With the tournament so close‚ this is only natural.\nYou’re too kind‚ Haruko-san. Don’t hold me back!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 180.8878579771,
      "endTime": 191.0378583586,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04-hrk007.m4a",
      "text": "……あはは、ごめんね\nでも、本当に心配だったから……大丈夫なら良かったわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Ahaha‚ sorry.\nBut I was really worried about you… I’m glad you’re okay.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 191.2482435539,
      "endTime": 199.1582436873,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04-rei011.m4a",
      "text": "……あの人達を見返すには優勝以外はないんですから\nもっとギリギリまで自分を追い込んで下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…We have to win if we want to show those girls what we’re made of.\nPush yourself to your limits.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 199.3686288828,
      "endTime": 209.3299438471,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04-hrk008.m4a",
      "text": "……うん、そうね。一緒に頑張りましょう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Yeah‚ you’re right. Let’s work hard together‚ okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 209.5403290425,
      "endTime": 214.1019843732,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04-hrk009.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ、はぁ……も、もう……動け、ないわ……っ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huff‚ huff… I-I can’t… move anymore…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 216.1790382698,
      "endTime": 225.5916910484,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04-rei012.m4a",
      "text": "……後は私が個人練してますから\n先に上がって下さい、お疲れ様です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I’ll do individual practice for the rest.\nYou should go ahead. Good work today.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 225.8020762438,
      "endTime": 233.7621442789,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04-hrk010.m4a",
      "text": "え？　でも……怜ちゃんも\nさすがに休んだ方がいいんじゃない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? But… Rei‚ you should\nrest too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 233.9725294743,
      "endTime": 240.80858408549997,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04-rei013.m4a",
      "text": "私は鍛え方が違うんです\n遙子さんと一緒にしないで下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I train differently.\nDon’t lump me in with you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 240.7333282471,
      "endTime": 246.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_04-hrk011.m4a",
      "text": "……少し休憩したら、また戻ってくるわ\n怜ちゃんも無理せず、ちゃんと休憩を挟んでね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I’ll come back after I take a short break.\nRei‚ don’t push yourself too hard. Make sure to take breaks.",
        "id": ""
